TENNIS - CHINA BEAT UZBEKISTAN 4 - 1 IN DAVIS CUP . China completed a 4 - 1 victory overUzbekistan in their Davis Cup Asia / Oceania zone group one , firstround tie after winning both reverse singles on Thursday . Results : Xia Jiaping beat Oleg Ogorodov 6 - 4 4 - 6 7 - 6 ( 7 - 5 ) 7 - 6 ( 9 - 7 ) Pan Bing beat Dmitry Tomashevich 6 - 4 7 - 6 ( 7 - 4 ) China now meet Japan or South Korea on April 4 to 6 for aplace in the qualifying tournament for the world group . 
